eu.ehri.project.models.annotations

Annotation Type Fetch


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Fetch
    Marks the entity pointed to by the framed Adjacency as one that should typically be fetched and displayed along with the master object.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Fields and Description
      static int DEFAULT_TRAVERSALS 

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String value
      The name of the relation when serialized.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean full
      Always serialize in full mode, regardless of whether lite serialization is enabled.
      int ifBelowLevel
      Only serialize this relationship if the depth of traversal is below this value.
      int ifLevel
      Only traverse this relationship at the specified level.
      int numLevels
      The number of levels this relationship should traverse from the current item.
      boolean whenNotLite
      Only serialize this relation when not serializing in 'lite' mode.

        public abstract String value
        The name of the relation when serialized.
        Returns:
        the relation name

      • ifBelowLevel

        public abstract int ifBelowLevel
        Only serialize this relationship if the depth of traversal is below this value. The default value is 10.
        Returns:
        the level below which this relationship should be traversed
        Default:
        10

      • ifLevel

        public abstract int ifLevel
        Only traverse this relationship at the specified level. Ignored if the level is less than 0.
        Returns:
        the level at which this relation should be traversed
        Default:
        -1

      • numLevels

        public abstract int numLevels
        The number of levels this relationship should traverse from the current item. i.e. if this item is at level N the serialization of it's relations should stop at level N + Fetch.numLevels().
        Default:
        -1

      • whenNotLite

        public abstract boolean whenNotLite
        Only serialize this relation when not serializing in 'lite' mode.
        Returns:
        to serialize or not
        Default:
        false

      • full

        public abstract boolean full
        Always serialize in full mode, regardless of whether lite serialization is enabled.
        Returns:
        override lite mode serialization
        Default:
        false
